Building with Maven
============
1. Ensure Maven is installed
2. Open a command window (Windows) or a terminal (Linux/Mac)
3. Run the following command:

	mvn tomcat:run

Import the project in Eclipse
=================
1. Ensure Maven is installed
2. Open a command window (Windows) or a terminal (Linux/Mac)
3. Run the following command:

	mvn eclipse:eclipse -Dwtpversion=2.0
